砰！时隔 39 年，凭借《Last Christmas》夺得圣诞节第一名https://www.nme.com/news/music/wham-christmas-number-one-2023-single-album-rolling-stones-3562902?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wham-christmas-number-one-2023-滚石乐队单曲Anagricel DuranFri, 22 Dec 2023 18:00:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3562902 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="英国伦敦威猛音乐会 - 1985 年，乔治·迈克尔和安德鲁·里奇利（摄影：Brian Rasic/Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “乔治会欣喜若狂，这么多年过去了，我们终于获得了圣诞节第一名”</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wham-christmas-number-one-2023-single-album-rolling-stones-3562902">威猛！</a>凭借《Last Christmas》在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首播<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wham-christmas-number-one-2023-single-album-rolling-stones-3562902">39 年后，凭借《Last Christmas》赢得圣诞节第一名</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="英国伦敦威猛音乐会 - 1985 年，乔治·迈克尔和安德鲁·里奇利（摄影：Brian Rasic/Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Wham-performing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/wham!">砰！</a> 39 年来，他们凭借标志性节日热门单曲《Last Christmas》赢得了圣诞节第一名。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/george-michael-obituary-1924150" target="_blank" rel="noopener">乔治·迈克尔讣告：1963-2016</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲由已故的乔治·迈克尔 (George Michael) 创作并制作，目标是在 1984 年登上圣诞排行榜第一名。然而，《Last Christmas》在发行后却被 Band-Aid 的《Do They Know It&#39;s Christmas?》挤下榜首。这首歌曲后来成为有史以来第二畅销单曲。</p><p>近四十年后的今天，《去年圣诞节》赢得了节日的头把交椅。砰！还创造了历史，创造了英国圣诞第一的最长旅程记录。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="砰！ - 去年圣诞节（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E8gmARGvPlI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在新闻稿中谈到官方排行榜上的成就时，Wham! 的安德鲁·里奇利 (Andrew Ridgeley) 表示：“《去年圣诞节》终于登上了备受珍视和追捧的官方圣诞节第一名，这一直是我们的主要目标。”</p><p>他继续说道：“经过这么多年，[我们]终于获得了圣诞节第一名，乔治一定会欣喜若狂。约格（乔治）说，他写《去年圣诞节》的目的是写一本圣诞节第一名。任务完成了！”</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/wham-last-christmas-number-1-andrew-ridgeley" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方排行榜公司的</a>数据，《去年圣诞节》在过去 7 天内的播放量达到惊人的 1330 万次，成为圣诞节期间播放量最高的圣诞节节目。它已成为英国历史上第三大歌曲，总销量达 534 万张，销量达 193 万张，播放量近 4.13 亿次。 </p><figure id="attachment_3562894" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3562894" style="width: 1900px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3562894" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/WHAMs-Andrew-Ridgeley-celebrates-Last-Christmas-claiming-2023s-Official-Christmas-Number-1-single-with-his-Official-Number-1-Award-from-Official-Charts-credit_-Official-Charts.jpg" alt="WHAM! 的安德鲁·里奇利 (Andrew Ridgeley) 庆祝去年圣诞节，获得了官方排行榜上的官方排名第一奖，并获得了 2023 年官方圣诞节排名第一的单曲。图片来源：官方图表" width="1900" height="2852" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/WHAMs-Andrew-Ridgeley-celebrates-Last-Christmas-claiming-2023s-Official-Christmas-Number-1-single-with-his-Official-Number-1-Award-from-Official-Charts-credit_-Official-Charts.jpg 1900w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/WHAMs-Andrew-Ridgeley-celebrates-Last-Christmas-claiming-2023s-Official-Christmas-Number-1-single-with-his-Official-Number-1-Award-from-Official-Charts-credit_-Official-Charts-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/WHAMs-Andrew-Ridgeley-celebrates-Last-Christmas-claiming-2023s-Official-Christmas-Number-1-single-with-his-Official-Number-1-Award-from-Official-Charts-credit_-Official-Charts-800x1201.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/WHAMs-Andrew-Ridgeley-celebrates-Last-Christmas-claiming-2023s-Official-Christmas-Number-1-single-with-his-Official-Number-1-Award-from-Official-Charts-credit_-Official-Charts-696x1045.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/WHAMs-Andrew-Ridgeley-celebrates-Last-Christmas-claiming-2023s-Official-Christmas-Number-1-single-with-his-Official-Number-1-Award-from-Official-Charts-credit_-Official-Charts-1392x2089.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/WHAMs-Andrew-Ridgeley-celebrates-Last-Christmas-claiming-2023s-Official-Christmas-Number-1-single-with-his-Official-Number-1-Award-from-Official-Charts-credit_-Official-Charts-1068x1603.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1900px) 100vw, 1900px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3562894" class="wp-caption-text"> WHAM! 的安德鲁·里奇利 (Andrew Ridgeley) 庆祝去年圣诞节，获得了官方排行榜上的官方排名第一奖，并获得了 2023 年官方圣诞节排名第一的单曲。图片来源：官方图表</figcaption></figure><p>过去一周，威猛！ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/christmas-number-one-2023-wham-the-pogues-sam-ryder-3561105">击败了 Sam Ryder、Mariah Carey 和 The Pogues ft. Kirsty MacColl、Elton John 等人，争夺圣诞节第一名的位置</a>。</p><p>在其他圣诞官方排行榜中，<a href="/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>凭借最新发行的专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-rolling-stones-hackney-diamonds-review-lyrics-tracklist-3515754">Hackney Diamonds</a> ”登上了圣诞专辑第一名的位置。</p><p>滚石乐队在新闻稿中专门对官方排行榜表示：“这是为 2023 年画上圆满句号的绝佳方式。感谢大家聆听 Hackney Diamonds 的演唱会。祝圣诞节和新年快乐！” </p><figure id="attachment_3562893" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3562893" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3562893" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Rolling-Stones-celebrate-their-Official-Number-1-album-with-Hackney-Diamonds-in-October-2023-credit_-Official-Charts.jpg" alt="滚石乐队于 2023 年 10 月与 Hackney Diamonds 庆祝他们的官方排名第一专辑。图片来源：官方排行榜" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Rolling-Stones-celebrate-their-Official-Number-1-album-with-Hackney-Diamonds-in-October-2023-credit_-Official-Charts.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Rolling-Stones-celebrate-their-Official-Number-1-album-with-Hackney-Diamonds-in-October-2023-credit_-Official-Charts-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Rolling-Stones-celebrate-their-Official-Number-1-album-with-Hackney-Diamonds-in-October-2023-credit_-Official-Charts-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Rolling-Stones-celebrate-their-Official-Number-1-album-with-Hackney-Diamonds-in-October-2023-credit_-Official-Charts-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Rolling-Stones-celebrate-their-Official-Number-1-album-with-Hackney-Diamonds-in-October-2023-credit_-Official-Charts-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Rolling-Stones-celebrate-their-Official-Number-1-album-with-Hackney-Diamonds-in-October-2023-credit_-Official-Charts-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3562893" class="wp